https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6R76M9OA5kvoL7syjavLvNexyd3.jpg The Central Park Concert is a two-disc DVD by the Dave Matthews Band. The album was recorded on September 24, 2003 on the Great Lawn of Central Park in New York, New York in front of a crowd of 121,382, the band's largest audience to date.
